{"tid":2245020,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"原來人大咗聽Eason嘅歌真係會喊","createTime":"2020-10-16T01:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T04:40:30.000Z","uid":55874,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0ebf9fed21b7380fb6300af98af048531dce34aa","tid":2245020,"uid":55874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:56:22.000Z","msg":"最佳損友<br />\n<br />\n從前共你促膝把酒傾通宵都不夠<br />\n我有痛快過你有沒有<br />\n很多東西今生只可給你<br />\n保守至到永久<br />\n別人如何明白透<br />\n實實在在踏入過我宇宙<br />\n即使相處到有過裂口<br />\n命運決定了以後再沒法聚頭<br />\n但說過去卻那樣厚<br />\n<br />\n沙龍<br />\n<br />\n登高峯一秒 得獎一秒<br />\n再破紀錄的一秒<br />\n港灣晚燈 山頂破曉<br />\n摘下懷念 記住美妙<br />\n升職那刻 新婚那朝<br />\n成為父母的一秒<br />\n要拍照的事 可不少<br />\n<br />\nShall we talk<br />\n<br />\n螢幕發光 無論什麼都看 <br />\n情人在分手邊緣只敢喝湯 <br />\n若沉默似金 還談什麼戀愛 <br />\n寧願在發聲機器面前笑著忙<br />\n<br />\n細個聽都知大個聽會更有感受，但到真係大個聽，先知道個種衝擊真係細個無法想像"},{"pid":"e5cf79322c73c4c0cdcfe4872461e67bd1a36c79","tid":2245020,"uid":269681,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T02:04:02.000Z","msg":"東京之旅一早比一世遙遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cee7ea4f075b148c95a2f5544461e8cda3c1fa4","tid":2245020,"uid":65353,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T02:10:47.000Z","msg":"陀飛輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十年前中學果陣純粹覺得好聽，十年後出到黎社會做野先明果種光陰飛逝既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab3e4966b4135a643f1dc35ccfedb47ce709f21","tid":2245020,"uid":197637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T02:16:17.000Z","msg":"藍到喊"},{"pid":"e84b3bd135417c2010f72abc3ae6fcac7ac149ea","tid":2245020,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T02:28:34.000Z","msg":"我的快樂時代"},{"pid":"8b512febb344dc7d2209ea84249e4f6defdcb6c5","tid":2245020,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T02:33:24.000Z","msg":"黃金時代"},{"pid":"7d89e7aed7176c218e0b384ae6f8ce0fa162f62d","tid":2245020,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T02:37:11.000Z","msg":"你給我聽好，歌詞屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明首歌一般但歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb11cab6ffef821ec0a12559504ff1b179b58cc","tid":2245020,"uid":55874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d89e7aed7176c218e0b384ae6f8ce0fa162f62d","tid":2245020,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T02:37:11.000Z","msg":"你給我聽好，歌詞屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明首歌一般但歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T03:22:14.000Z","msg":"還會有人讓你睡不著 <br />\n還能為某人燃燒 <br />\n我親愛的這樣浪漫的煎熬 <br />\n不是想要就能要別炫耀"},{"pid":"1587b589acadc6e2c027ad34e8977588d19f0276","tid":2245020,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"我不好愛<br />\n<br />\n你又美麗 又偉大 又這麼慷慨<br />\n我被厚待 亦相當意外<br />\n給你寵愛 這戀愛 結果倒下來<br />\n大概只是 我不好愛<br />\n我又憤怒 又脆弱 固執不會改<br />\n怕被冷落 卻不肯接待<br />\n給你寵愛 這戀愛 愛不出未來<br />\n大概都是 我不好愛<br />\n<br />\n其實唔係伴侶對自己差 只係自己唔識得去愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}